help
	<dcbHelp: 'Help center'>
	<dcbIcon: #icon>
	<dcbOpen: #openHelp>
	^ 'I am the widget used to browse user help.

The left list contains all the tools documented. Simply click on any item to have the documentation displayed in the text field on the right.

For each item in the list, the icon displayed is used in any menu anywhere in the system.'